-- TEXT: Madoff plea statement
-- 
-- Fri Mar 13, 2009 12:33pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/13/us-madoff-text-sb-idUSTRE52B6C520090313

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Bernard Madoff pleaded guilty on Thursday to charges he orchestrated the biggest financial swindle in Wall Street history and was ordered to jail to await a sentence that could last the rest of his life. 

 Madoff's prepared plea allocution statement was provided by the law firm Dickstein & Shapiro and can be seen by clicking  here The criminal information, provided by the U.S. attorney's office can be found  here